I take 1-2 dummies before bed or after work, and it usually takes about 20-30 minutes for me to start feeling the affects. For me it helps me to relax. I sell insurance for a living an it can be stressful. My mind is constantly racing. Hence, eating a couple dummies each night helps me to slow down and do exactly as the package says - CHILL! Because of this, I sleep deeply and wake up refreshed. My mind isn't racing when I sleep. I highly recommend this product, but do not use while driving or while working. Use before going to bed or if you simply nee to wind down.

This morning I had to give up and just pour it into my juice.  I don't like the taste so I add it to juice.  There is quite a bit of solids in the bottle, it is not totally liquid, I am not sure if this is normal or not since it is my first time ordering it and using it, but I do like the results I am getting with sleep and less chronic pain.

Most have a bitter after taste, and I was very pleased to find that these really taste good; especially for the way it calms and promotes a sense of well being. These are very good... title: Good
author: Collin
body:
I bought 1000mg of the blueberry flavor and it was a good buy with a big discount. I think I got something like 20 or 30% off. The reason it was good and not great was the crystals were in huge chunks and sat at the bottom of the tincture until the very drop was done.

Once all the liquid was gone, I shattered open the bottle and ate all the crystals at once and that's where all of the BANG was... I don't think the crystals should be huge chunks and sit at the bottom, I feel that if they should be finely dusted into the mixture to get an even more even mix throughout.

Good product, could be great. Will be trying other items, not sure about buying this one again.

author: Mary Jane
body: Normal sour snakes are my favorite anyway. So when I saw the CBD infused sour snakes, they were the ones I knew I had to try first! They taste amazing, much better than some brands of gummy worms that I have tried. Others have said that the amount of gummies was disappointing, but they are so strong that I can really only eat one at a time. Keep a bag of normal ones handy, though! It's really difficult to eat only one.

title: Perfect for sharing and gifts!
author: Mary Jane
body: These are super chewy and tasty! They're sour, but not unbearably so. The sugar crystals make them a bit sour, but the gooey part is sweet. These would be the perfect gift for my friends that work all the time and those who like to diet because they are potent without the added guilt of large candies.

title: Helpful for work and relaxing
author: Mary Jane
body: Super fun to eat, and even more fun with the CBD effects! The sour coating gives a new dimension to the flavor, making it feel like more candy than just one kind. They help me to keep my anxiety calm at work, and relax at the end of the day. I will definitely reorder and recommend these to friends!

title: Yummy, Soothing, Satisfying Gummies!!
author: Mary Jane
body: These sweet gummy worms are really surprisingly good. Always fresh and munchie, they have an ever so slight aftertaste, but in consideration of the relaxing effect they deliver, these wormies cannot be beat... I will be definitely be ordering more!! :)

title: ABSOLUTELY SUPERB!!
author: Marisol Elwell
body: I dont know how else to say it. These Watermelon slices are just absolutely the perfect relaxing treat. EXTREMELY effective, and perfect ly delicious. These are my all time favorite!!

title: Actually VERY GOOD!
author: Critical Skeptic
body: These rainbow bites are very tasty. There is practically zero aftertaste, and they deliver a potent CBD wave of chilling relaxation. The quality is superb, and for something that works so good, they sure taste great! I was reading the other review, and just wanted to also say... Mine arrived in good order. It wasn't "in a million pieces".... Not sure what shes complaining about, though. I LOVE to have a million pieces of these, lol.

title: ONE OF MY FAVORITES
author: Critical Skeptic
body: These are definitely one of my top pics. Of the 'not' sugar sprinkled or sour selections, I believe this is probably the best tasting... But then I taste another... I am really blown away at how good and EFFECTIVE these tasty, pleasing, treats really are.

title: BY FAR the Best Worms in the Garden!!!
author: Skeptical Critic
body: I am just loving these. Not that many in a bag, but once you devour a couple you will clearly know why. The sweet taste is deceptive. The strength and quality here is premium!! Will be ordering more of these for certain!!

title: Most Chillin' Fruit on the Web!!
author: Marisol Elwell
body: These fruit treats are really yummy. Its amazing how something so effective can taste so good, really. It still doesn't beat my watermelon slices, but man oh man are they effective at helping me enter a state of relaxation after a hard day. Just totally Awesome. I LOVE Diamond CBD's line.

title: Hard to Believe This Stuff is Legal... Seriously!
author: Critical Skeptic
body: It is JUST THAT GOOD. Its really mind-blowing to me that these products are still so under discovered. The release of tension that comes as a result of puffing on these makes me whole-heartedly comprehend why Big Pharma fights to keep this stuff out of the hands of those that need it. With as effective as this is, I don't know how many of these benzo producing pharmaceutical companies wouldn't take too substantial of a hit. I only wish i would have learned of these a LONG time ago. Try this, just one time... As people continue discovering these, they won't be able to keep these on the shelf. The taste is totally satisfying.

title: I LOVE THESE!! CANT BELIEVE HOW THEY WORK...
author: Skeptical Critic
body:
These are like your regular gummy rings, tasty, fresh, and soft. Except... What a sweet sensation of relaxation!!! I have eaten a LOT of candies over the years, and I have to say... I have never eaten candy that made me feel so, pleased for the consuming of something beneficial for my health, and just straight up relaxed and at ease. Where have these been all my life?

I LOVE THEM!! <3

author: Mercedes
body: Enjoying the benefits of these yummy gummies as we speak. First time buyer and I took one gummy, after 20 min I felt relaxation take over my body and my muscle spasms  diminish :) Def recommend can't wait to try more

body:
I have hesitantly tried these gummie bears and have been ordering them ever since. I am amazed at how it completely relieves my arthritis pain in my hands and shoulder. I have had constant nausea and nothing gave me relief. I  have used prescription meds, inject able steroids, and pain killers, all t no avail. I could never get a complete restful night sleep until these came into my daily routine. They even  cured a migraine headache!! This is my Miracle drug, I am AMAZED at all the healing abilities this gives.  I have not felt this good in years! Keep up the good research and work. I am a lifer with Gummie  Bears. 
Signed, a VERY happy customer. Liberetta

body: This is my first exposure to CBD. I purchased this oil, and DABS. (I still have not tried this item, not really sure what to do with it). The label directions say to "Shake well", but I seem to have a problem doing that. Also, not sure of how much to use at each dose. I have been using a full dropper, and I do think it helps with my pain. (I have had back pain for most of my 57 years).This is an odd flavor, but not horrible. I think my next purchase I will go with a fruity flavor. Yes, I will continue to purchase !!!

body: This tastes great and works great. I have really bad anxiety and chronic pain from a variety of issues / disabilities and this has really helped. I am not completely pain free, but I am able to function better than I was previously. Plus I am more relaxed and that has helped with my anxiety.

title: Best in Quality & Efficacy
author: Richard Allen
body:
I've tried a few brands & Diamond CBD is the best in taste, effect & quality. The reason why I wanted to try it is because I have COPD. Unknowingly, I had purchased CBIS stock a fews years ago, no profits yet, but a recent stock update reported on new CBD inhaler to hit the market. Being impatient I wanted to try the CBD vape oil & it helped immediately! I was pretty amazed to say the least & highly recommend trying it. I bought 1st bottle 25mg & it worked immediately.
My 2ond order from the 1st company wasn't quite the same as the first & my 3rd order was from yet another distributor & the product was ok, but
I was still searching for more info & stumbled on this web site. The price was reasonable & selection better than anything else I've seen.
The shipping was fast & free! The flavor & quality was far superior than the others I've tried. Last, the packaging itself puts this product in league above the rest. 
Definitely Top Shelf!

author: Perry
body: This product helps me a lot. Just be sure you read and understand how much product you are really getting. The advertising is deceptive. The picture shows around 2 dozen gummy bears, but you only get 6 per package. They do state that in the description, but I was initially disappointed thinking I had been shorted on my order.

title: AMAZING!!
author: ARI / freepieceofmind (IG)
body: I bought these gummies as my first every CBD gummy trial. They tasted amazing! Exactly like the candy and no gross after taste. You would have no idea there's CBD infused! I suffer from anxiety, depression, and massive migraines so I often take medications to relieve this. Instead I decided to try these gummies. I had a headache and once the gummy settled in, i noticed the tension was eased. I also noticed my hands weren't shaking, which is what happens when my anxiety attack are in the beginning stages. The general relief of these problems with one single product has made me the happiest I've been in awhile. My boyfriend also tried them and he said they helped relieve the pressure in his knee (it's a long story) which is unbelievable because no anti-inflammatory can relieve his pain like how these gummies did. My only complaint is the quantity in the bag, but the effects of the product are completely worth the price. Will definitely experiment with others soon!

title: CBD oil 1000 MG is the best on the market
author: Marco
body: I have been using this CBD natural flavor 1000 mg since March 2017. Since getting into my car accident last year my neck & shoulder pain & spasms were making me miserable. I was taking a lot of spasms medications at a rate of 4 times a day.Since taking this CBD product I no longer take my medication for the spasms. Also it is  fantastic in helping me sleep. You must take it constantly everyday. Give it time to enter your body and work its magic. You will not regret it. Thank you Diamond CBD for a quality & awesome product.

title: Very disappointed
author: Cel
body: Product arrived liquified and although I have sent two emails to customer service requesting a refund no one has responded. Also the picture if the product shows many gummy bears the package I received was tiny. Description text shows quantity of 6. Pictures and product descriptions are conflicting. Buyer be ware.

title: Calm, but not drugged
author: Napoleon's mom
body: My babe is such a wild, hyper, crazy little one. I was really cautious trying this for the first time, because I didn't want him to look strung out. He really liked the flavor, and I was surprised with the results. He wasn't too tired, and he didn't bark as much at neighbors. He played more easily with my parents dogs, and he was so loving and sweet. I will definitely use it from now on with him.

title: So, so tasty
author: Candy
body: This tastes so good, just like the real thing. It's amazing having oil that has all my medical marijuana benefits and tastes just like the plant without having to worry about black lungs or surprise drug tests. I didn't think this was possible! I will definitely order again, and I will enjoy every last drop. "Impressed" doesn't cover the excitement I feel about it.

title: Stellar Product!
author: Chris
body: The simple answer is YES, it works! I drive 1500 or more miles each week to support a large hospital system, and have had insomnia for several years. I just couldn't turn my brain off. Plus, I have 2 small children at home, and they make my insomnia ever the worse. I've been on several sleep aids, which have worked, but... they make me black out. If I'm on call, and my pager goes off at 2am, the hypnotic sleep aid works so well that I can barely function enough to get out of bed. My wife hated it. I too hated it. So, I sought out the best replacement I could find. Cannabis is not state legal here, and I'm sure the hospital would frown upon me using it. The CBD products available however, are legal. So, after about $700 spent on various CBD items, I finally found liquid gold. It is BY FAR the best product I've used to date. As a vape juice, it's perfect. Flavor is wonderful, and most importantly, it allows me to turn off my brain at night and go to sleep, while still being able to function if I get paged over night. A+ rating. This stuff truly is liquid gold. Thank you!!!

author: Lindsey
body: First let me say as someone who has spent months trying different products I can say this is the only brand I will even try anymore. Everyone one is different and reacts different but this did nothing for me. Not even a little. Chill gummies have been the only thing so far that have the desired effect.

body: I ordered a 250 mg bottle of raspberry lemonaid oil. Not sure what they sent me, but it came in a bottle that (from the Diamond CBD website) looked exactly like their vape refills (green body and gold top cap and dropper system). Sent an email request for information 5 days ago and never got a respoanse. Now waiting on another order (for 550mg of orange ice cream oil), but who knows what they will send me. Very unlikely that I'll buy from them again. Apparently they are far more concerned with customers' money than customers' satisfaction.

body: I have had anxiety since I was born.  Trying to overcome or deal with it my whole life has not been fun.  Now with more and more electronics available and the increase in EMF and RF waves I feel this is another major factor that contributes to my anxiety.  I have been so grateful to find Diamond CBD because this is the first all natural oil that actually works.  I like it a lot as it takes maybe only five to 10 minutes until I feel relaxed again.  If helps with insomnia also.  In general I feel better, and I can tell you it also helps my right foot from neuropathy issues from surgery.  I don't get the tingling in it anymore.  Thank you guys at Diamond!

title: Label Mixup, but all good
author: Rigel R.
body: After clearing up a packaging confusion* I used the oil. Same consistency as other 100mg oils I've purchased, great taste (not harshly fake or chemical like a lot of watermelon, but very floral.) Works as expected at this concentration. Still flavor hopping, but will definitely buy in this concentration again and I recommend it to anyone with low to moderate stress/anxiety. One full dropper keeps me chill for a whole day, a few drops take the edge off if I'm starting to feel weird suddenly. *Diamond called me to let me know that they are in the process of changing their bottling and packaging. I received the frosted green bottle with a green cap that has been used to identify their vape additives. The bottle also had the vape additive label, which specifies 'Do Not Drink' (use as oral drops.) Initially I was upset, and it took about a week for them to address my inquiry, but they cleared it up. I actually like the frosted bottles much better - they leak less and are much easier to open than the clear bottle's black dropper lids.

The 2nd time,I gave 2 vials of the dropper and she was relaxed for hours. I'll try 3 next time to see how she reacts to that. I'm trying to find the right amount for her (she's 85 lbs) and for her tolreance before her surgery. This would be AMAZING for anxious dogs(separation anxiety, storms, etc). Maybe just a small (25%-50% of recomended doseage) to help take hte edge off.

title: Sooo sleepy
author: Shinko
body:
For the life of me, I could NOT get the bottle to twist open.
I was having so much trouble getting the bottle open, but the lady I spoke to on the phone earlier said to run it under hot water. Did the trick.
It smells like watermelon, but tastes like watermelon flavored sour patch kids candy as another reviewer mentioned. 
I took about 6 drops around 2:20 today and around 2:30, I started feeling the effects.
At the moment, my mind feels heavy and my body is relaxed. I just want to close my eyes and sleep. Lol.
I don't think it was a good idea to test this out so early in the day though since it's my 1st time taking any kind of CBD oil, but definitely works.
One con I have to mention, there's a kind of aftertaste. Like licking perfume. 
I dunno if this is common after taking CBD oil though since I have nothing to compare it to.
Still, the initial flavor and effects of this CBD oil outweigh the aftertaste.

I got the 150 mg. I get migraines every so often, back pains, still suffering from a torn ligament in my ankle from 2 1/2 yrs ago, neck pains... Etc.

Will definitely try out other flavors though once I run out.

body: This CBD Additive has been the best CBD product I or anyone I know have ever come across to date. I have tried every CBD Vape juice on the market and when this one came out it blew them all out of the water. There are many people with severe illnesses that do not have access to legal alternatives to aid in their suffering and this product helps more than most of their prescribed medications put together. Unfortunately, the pharmaceutical drug industry is trying to criminalize the medicinal and recreational use of CBD even though it is 100% legal and does not contain any synthetic or DEA scheduled ingredients. However, a few months after the initial roll out, the quality/strength went down a bit, but was still the best CBD product on the market. If diamond CBD can stick to the original formula and price, they will have no competition. Also, many of their loyal customers are currently wondering and worries why they have been out of stock in most retail stores in certain markets and here online. Hopefully, whatever issue is causing the shortage will be resolved soon. Thanks for your wonderful product!

title: Hopeful!
author: Angela J.
body: The reason why it's a 4 is simple because of the bottle design. Because you have to push down instead of squeeze, my hands tend to get oil on them and spill over the bottle and my hands when using it as an oral drop. The squeeze dropper would eliminate that since I wouldn't have to brace it. I often feel like a junky since I often lick my hand in order to not waste the product. (yes I'm weird.) - Overall a great product. I have used 100mg for my anxiety and my mom uses 200mg for pain. However it wasn't enough so I went up to 350mg. Hopefully she'll get some relief with that. I have had a great response. It doesn't make me chill out so to speak, but it does help quiet those negative, self depricating thoughts. Even when I get them, it doesn't weigh as much as it once did. While I didn't expect it to cure me, if I don't take it for a day or two, I certainly get the thoughts again and it sucks. It's interesting to actually know the difference of being on vs off of it though. My mom took the extreme cbd oil first. While not on the page, I was told by diamond that it was 200mg. This did very little for my mom who suffers from chronic pain due to complications with lupus and arthritis. We only just got the 350mg because of the delay due to the 2017 Aug hurricanes but I'm hopeful that she'll see good results soon.

title: Not sure about these
author: Concerned Buyer
body: I picked up a pack of the diamond cbd chill sour faces extreme strength gummies and find it troublesome that you include an "enjoy at your own risk" clause on the package. Also it says to limit use to 1-2 pieces every 6 hours...why is this if it has no psychoactive properties? The package is really nice and it seemed credible yet on reddit users report abnormalities after ingesting this product. And it says you get your hemp from Scandinavia yet on the package it states that it is made in the usa. Conflicting things for one who seeks peace, do you have any comment?

title: Great Product, Very Poor Customer Service
author: Chelsea
body:
Let me start by saving I love this company's products. I use them for pain relief and consider them a necessary part of my life. I ordered a bottle of this oil during the Labor Day sale and it was 50% off. Yay, right?! Wrong. They sent me the regular 15 ml bottle of their oil and not this larger, 30 ml bottle. They sent me the wrong product. I emailed them about it two weeks ago  and got an automated response saying I'd get an actual response from a support rep within 24-48 hours. I got a reply 7 days later which required me to respond back. It's been 7 more days and I'm waiting on a response from them. They are 2 weeks into this issue now and still haven't cleared it up. I'll be contacting the Better Business Bureau.

Buyers beware if you order anything from this company during a sale. I have ordered gummies in the past and received a variety that was different from the one I ordered but I never complained because I technically received the same amount of CBD that I ordered. The experience with this oil has forced me to cut off business with this company (I was a regular customer) and take my hard-earned money elsewhere. What is the point  of having 50% off sales if you are going to rip your customers off by only sending them 50% of the product they ordered and not working to fix the issue?

title: Contains Synthetic Cannabinoids
author: Adrian S.
body: I kept quiet about this during my 2 month period of everyday use because i didn't want to ruin it for others. But i am on day 4 of cessation of use from the vape additive/liquid gold. I knew the whole time this stuff contains a yet-to-be-illegalized synthetic cannabinoid. Cbd alone will not get you high like this stuff does. I am currently undergoing heavy withdrawals involving cold sweats during unrestful sleep, erectile dysfunction, diarrhea, lack of appetite, and inability to concentrate or multi-task. I quit because 1. This stuff is like cannabinoid crack and 2. After some time, when i would vape this stuff and lay down, i suddenly couldn't breath through my nose and would get a pain in my heart area, indicating either a disruption in blood flow, an allergic reaction to the drug it contains, or both. Please be aware this is not just cbd. This review may get removed but i hope it does not.

title: Product Change
author: Kristianna M.
body: I have bought Diamond CBC from a local shop where I live and recently decided to buy directly from Diamond instead. My first delivery was late and both bottles were busted. The new order arrived in good condition however, I am not sure if the product ingredients have changed or what the difference is but the affects from Diamond and the affects from my local shop are totally different. It's like night and day. I prefer whatever Diamond product my local shop has over the product directly from Diamond. I would say I would buy from Diamond again directly but I would probably purchase a completely different product compared to what I recently and normal buy and will stick to purchasing my Diamond vape additive from my local shop. Diamond is still a fantastic product, I am just not satisfied with the results from the item I purchased through the distributer. title: Diamond is this girl’s best friend!
author: Stephanie B.
body: I have educated myself extensively on CBD. There are lots of companies out there. Free trials aren’t really free! The first oil I tried (another company)was good but tasted awful! So I began looking for flavored oil, and found this in cotton candy! It was so good that I ordered another the day I received it! I got offers for half off, that made it affordable to purchase gummies, and vape oil, and ordered those as well! I have an autoimmune disorder (Myalgic encephalomyelitis) and Stage 4 metastatic Cervical/uterine cancer, that contributed to djd pain in all of my joints. I will not make some cray cray claim that it cures cancer, and neither does diamond! But, it certainly does help with side effects of treatment, and the disease process itself such as inflammation. Whether you choose flavored oil, to use sublingual, in an e cig or else, it’s amazing! I can’t say enough great things about the website, promo codes and customer service! They keep you informed from the minute you order! I’ve ordered trial offers, from other companies, I’ve never heard from again! But NO MORE! I have found my home for CBD. I am now considering opening a shop, in this one horse town, to help others. I know what we do have available here, has mediocre quality and awful taste! Give it a try, you will easily find a flavor you like fruity, chocolate,’cereal, candy, etc! Something for everyone, even pets!

body: Been purchasing and using the diamond CBD vape additive they sell here for $90 for quite some time and have had wonderful results. Decided to buy a bottle of this for $170 and give it a try. Zero effect at all. Complete waste of money. Called and talked to customer service and they didn't want to do much to help me at all and acted like there was no possibility I could have received a bad batch or something. I did find a solution no thanks to Diamond CBD staff, so there's hope for any of you that ever get a bad bottle of CBD. I started to believe that maybe the decarboxylation process this company was utilizing might not be converting the CBD to the form needed for higher end low heat vape pens....Think subvod.  I happen to own an Ardent decarboxylation device so I figured I was already screwed by Diamond CBD not being willing to send me a new bottle so rather than just throw it away....Why not try decarbing it myself? Holy crap!!!  Now it's easily the most potent CBD I've ever tried. I'm going to start decarbing every product I get from this company so I can REALLY get my money's worth. Clearly Diamond CBD needs to look in to the process (if any) they are using to decarb their CBD. I thought maybe that was because they expected everyone to vape at super high heat, but they also claim this can be used sublingually so that would require decarbing the product.

I stumbled across the benefits of CBD while researching what could help my mood as I’m hitting menopause, I’ve also had adhd my entire life.  There wasn’t much research in cbd and menapause, but I gave it a try.   I am extremely thankful I did.

I use the oil and relax gummies during the day, the Chong and chill at night.  Over the past couple months my mood swings have gone away.  PMS is much better, focus is better as well. 

Work colleagues have notice my focus and mood as well.

I’m so in love with this company and products, I bought their stock!!!

Thank you!!   To anyone hesitating to try it.  Just go for it. I now use the oils, gummies and pain cream, any product I’ve ordered... I bought again

title: Stop looking, seriously, AMAZING STUFF.  Diamond CBD stepped up too........
author: Jack
body:
Well, I have tried quite literally over 200 brands and over 100 sites.  This is probably some of the most potent CBD I have ever tried(for me).  I have no cartilage in either knee & am only 35.  Military played hell on my knees and back.  This stuff is tremendous to mix in at night with your E Juice.  CAUTION, I would start out light..This stuff is strong and will accomplish relaxation, comfort and eventually sound sleep.  I will say I had some very vivid dreams first four or five nights of vaping this before bed.  I dont leave reviews, but, I felt compelled to do so since there are so many garbage CBD companies out there that still money and send you straight crap.  

Diamond CBD screwed the shipping up from the start, took nearly 3 weeks to get my stuff(right after holidays).  BUT they made it right.  They waived all expedited shipping and sent me an extra bottle of gummies, plus quick responses.  The customer service combined with this unmatched CBD(in my experience) is why I will be a customer for life!

title: In a Class of its Own
author: David M.
body: Diamond CBD Vape Additive simply has no rivals among the ever-growing list of companies wanting to sell you a CBD Vape Additive. Actually, Diamond CBD sits apart from all other CBD products. Its effects are dramatically different and vary depending upon your mood, the concentration you vape it at, whether you are working or resting, etc. If you just want something that resembles being “stoned”, go for the others, if you want something to enlighten, only Diamond CBD Vape will put you on that path. An illustration: I vape nicotine. However, I always add two droppers full of Diamond CBD Vape Additive to each 4ml of nicotine oil. First, the additive helps it calms that edgy, somewhat irritating feeling vaping nicotine often leaves you with. Second, I have been using Diamond CBD Vape Additive with my nicotine for about one year and it has helped me to better control my mania (I am Uni-polar Manic), that is, it has greatly reduced the incidents of anger and rage associated with a manic in crisis, a manic in crisis is all anger and rage, a manic under control is usually a highly productive problem solver. (David M Martin, *******, GA)

body: I bought a bottle of the Preium Infused Liquid 100mg - 30ml, CBD oil in Feb (it was in a black tubular box then). I recently reached for it again & noticed some dark globs floating around in the bottle. I managed to fish a piece out (thinking it was mold) and it looked like fused crystallized brown sugar!!!  Has anyone experi fed this?  Is this normal?  Is that the CBD separating from the oils?  I’m scared to use it again. Works well but I have no idea what those globs of brown stuff are!!

title: the exact gummies that were adulterated with 5F-ADB
author: rivers
body:
these were tested in june of 2017 and found to contain 5F-ADB, a powerful synthetic cannabinoid designed to get people high and has been linked to at least one death. also it's Schedule 1, making it fully illegal in the US.

here is the picture of the lab result:
https://imgur.com/a/OmPaj

diamondCBD claims that they've tested this product for synthetic cannabinoids and that it's clean, but if you look at the lab results you will see that they specifically did not test for 5F-ADB. very convenient.

title: Disappointed in customer service
author: Michael Guy
body:
Extremely disappointed in customer service....

I ordered 1000mg in 30ml because that's what the website said, I called to confirm and customer service told me, 1000mg was in 30ml, I ordered the watermelon and raspberry,  and I got 15ml...called, got a ups return label,  was told they would send 30ml, after I shipped my product back,  I saw a text after i sent it back claiming 1000mg doesn't come in 30ml, but 500mg did, well I saw it here, 500mg is still at 15ml on the website. So the claim that I saw it there is false, I never looked at anything but the 1000mg...I felt I got the bait and switch and they are out of integrity and accountability....the product smelled great through the bottle but I was not happy with the outcome....the money returned in my cc after they get it,  I would prefer the product and a much better review, but until that happens, this is where I stand....Very very disappointed.....

My episodes would last 6-8 hours at a time, and include severe stomach pain and vomiting, even on the strongest medication my doctor would prescribe. I had lost over 20 lbs. As a last resort, I picked up some Diamond CBD and became a vaper. Since starting 2 months ago, I have reduced my episodes down to less than once a week, and have only vomited one time. I know this product cannot be sold as a medication, but it is a miracle "drug" for me. It saved my life.

title: Great Product
author: Rachael H.
body: I was not sure what to expect from this product. The initial bitter taste was quickly chased by the familiar and pleasant gummi bear flavors from my childhood. At first nothing happened but within fifteen to twenty minutes I found that I was experiencing a pleasant warming sensation in my hands, feet and belly. I felt calm, good , literally chill. On the nights that I ate these gummis before bed, I slept deeply and 'didn't wake up in the middle of the night like I often do. On nights when my mind would not shut off and I would lay awake in bed running the days events over and over, I ate this product and fell asleep easily. When I ate them in the afternoons when I was feeling down or sad I felt the pleasant warming sensation laid on my couch took an hour nap and woke up feeling refreshed and ready to finish out my day. My husband also ate them and he reported to me similar feelings of "chill" and improved ability to fall asleep and stay asleep. Which is wonderful for him as he works with a schedule that has him on nights and days at random times. An excellent product for people who don't know much about CBD, It was a wonderful first time experience. If I had a lot of cash I would buy these often and make them a part of my life on a regular basis.

title: VAPE ADDITIVE - Made me feels stoned
author: Sheri Leland
body:
I love the vape additive however when I take 2-3 vape hits at one time, I feel very stoned and my heart starts palpitating.  I'm in recovery and if it's true active CBD oil that's one thing . On a CBD oil Facebook Page I commented how great your brand is, and she sent me the link to her review questioned A. If it has THC in it (it shows 0.3%) not much . But she had it analyzed at a independent lab and the synthetic form of Marijuana called Spice was highly suspected .

I' called you about this about a month ago and left a voicemail but nobody ever called back. PLEASE tell me the truth . I love the cream but the "maximum strength" additives are getting me stoned for about 30 minutes . My sobriety is everything to me!!

Sheri L

title: This helps better than medication

body: So I've always struggle with anxiety and depression since I was young. I also recently found out I have PCOS so I'm in constant pain all the time and it's added to my depression since it makes it 100x harder to become pregnant, and some of the other symptoms make me feel down about myself as well. I hate the medication I was on, it just made me feel like a walking zombie and all I did was sleep my life away. Then, one of our friends recommend that we try a CBD product because it works for their pain and their depression. I was a little skeptical, but I just sucked it up and ordered a couple bags of these gummies and let me tell you I'm GLAD I did. After about ten minutes I felt it kick in and instantly felt the switch in my brain go off. Everything was quiet and my pain was pretty much non existent. I'm able to fall right to sleep without having a million thins run threw my mind. I'd recommend these to anyone! I love them and I'm glad I found them!

title: It's Magic

body: I hope you don't think I'm crazy.  I can't believe this myself.  I have been having so much pain in my neck, back, etc. causing pinched nerves.  I never get a complete night's sleep because of the pain.  Now this is unbelievable!  Last night before bed, my partner encouraged me to just "try it."  Now here is the miracle.  I slept the whole night without pinched nerves keeping me awake.  This morning...no pain.  Is this possible?  I can't believe it myself.  Is it all in my head?  I'm typing this without pain.  A miracle on Easter Sunday.  Thank you.

title: The ingredients list is wrong on the website
author: Anna H
body:
The product is wonderful but this webpage needs to be fixed.  I ordered these because they seemed to be the only CBD gummy I could find without corn products in them.  Corn products cause me pain and eating them to treat my pain is just counterproductive.  I contacted support about the problem but it seems like the list is now even more wrong, saying it has cocoa in it now.  
The real list off the package:
Sugar, Invert Sugar, Corn Syrup, Modified Corn Starch,  Tartaric Acid, Citric Acid, Natural and Artifical flavors, Tetum Dioxide, FD&C Yellow #5, Red #40, FD&C Blue #1, Alcohol, Industrial Hemp Cannabidiol (CBD), Melatonin, and proprietary blend extract.

title: SELL BATTERIES AND CHARGING ACCESSORIES THAT MATCHUP WITH VAPE TANKS!
author: JOHN
body: It only makes sense to sell battery packs that matchup with your vape tanks!  There are a lot of first time users who need the complete package to enjoy your products!  That's another item to profit from... ?  There are a lot of different battery sizes and attachments out there, and not all are interchangeable!  Make it easy for your customers, and they will come back!  Also makes sense to sell chargers as well... One stop shopping experience!  You could also offer different varieties of vape tanks... complete w/ battery & chargers?  If not... you could lose customers to your competitors who have it all... ready to enjoy?  I am a shareholder of POTN and just putting in my 2 cents to help generate more sales revenue, and keep customers happy!  The last thing you want is for them to get frustrated trying to find the right battery hook-up... lose money!  Coming from an investors point of view with constructive ideas and solutions to an obvious over-sight by management?

This pen had leaked inside pouch. Pen would not light up until the leakage had dried out. It finally somewhat works, but burns unevenly so I cough quite a bit and the vape leaves a stickier residue in my throat. Item tastes pleasant, it's easy to use, and the company is awesome, not so much the shipping method.

title: How this product is changing my life
author: Leana E.
body: I have been taking the the CBD oil for a couple of months now. When first purchasing it I had a lighter dosage, the second order i upped the ante by buying a higher dosage at 450. The third order i purchased the 1000 mg - i couldnt order anything in between that because there were not any to order between the 550 and 750. So i settled for the 1000 mg. I will be receiving it by the end of this week, so hopefully this will be another stage of repairing an incurable disorder that I have. The disorder is FSP - Familial Spastic Paraparesis - it is the crippling of movement of your legs. At any rate, I do think from taking this CBD Oil - I am getting stronger in the left leg where I have better balance with it. I have been blessed because my right leg seems to be all right. So with me hoping for the best with this CBD Oil and the Good Lord - my this become a curable disorder with your product. Amen!! Thanks for the 35% off coupon on this review because I will definitely reorder the 1000 mg and at the cost on the next purchase that will be very helpful in the overall cost. Love all the flavors also, I decided to get vanilla on my last purchase. Leana Elam

title: I admit, I'm still dialing

body: I admit, I'm still dialing in the strength that's best for me, so having such a wide variety available in one place has been a great help. Shipping is always lightning fast, and never leaves me wondering where my purchase is. The flavor on this specific product was pretty good - no aftertaste and a texture close to the standard candy ribbons. Not only will I be continuing to shop with diamond, these gummies are in my top three.

I will probably order again as this is my first bad experience but I am not happy with this particular experience. Fingers crossed that this was a fluke.
